    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/battlestars-daybreak-worst-ending-history-screen-science-fiction#comment-10229" class="active">A successful Luddite ending</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="http://welcometosherwood.wordpress.com" rel="nofollow">Steve Zeoli</a> (not verified) on Fri, 2009-08-07 10:29.</div>
