<p>(c) The Eye of Jupiter painted by Kara Thrace describes a 'String' at the centre of a black hole. A singularity, for those who know their string theory, is a point of change in possibility. The String at the centre is debris of change in possibility. -Cue the fleet jumping that singularity so that the 'think they are hippies' listening to the watchtower music are all gathered in a room on the Galactica and the 'fifth cylon' magically appears in the room surrounded by Tory, Tyrol, Tigh, and Anders as they emerge from the jump point.</p>
