    <h3 class="title"><a href="/battlestar/battlestars-daybreak-worst-ending-history-screen-science-fiction#comment-9995" class="active">RE: The worst ending in the history of on-screen science fiction</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by <a href="http://isitchristmas.com" rel="nofollow">Prolescum</a> (not verified) on Tue, 2009-07-14 03:27.</div>
